<mxCell id="p1n45" value="Explicit NON-entities: no Society table, no society_id, no tenancy (single society per deployment). &#x27;defaulter&#x27; derived at read time, never stored. The four books are views over ONE append-only journal. Vendors are records, not users. No Razorpay webhook/settlement entity — outcome is Payment + ledger postings." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;spacing=6;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1540" y="435" width="240" height="160" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
