<mxCell id="p7n6" value="State machine: submitted → verified (designated employee) → approved | rejected → paid. Approval = majority of the designated EC subset. A single rejection is terminal (discards approvals); override = majority of the ENTIRE EC; resubmission = fresh invoice via resubmission_of (closes the override window). Payment posts Expense Ledger + Bank/Cash Book." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;spacing=6;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="440" y="486" width="380" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
