<mxCell id="p8n2" value="File bytes in S3 (FileBucket, presigned up/download); metadata row in Postgres. File is IMMUTABLE once uploaded — correction = new document + archive old. No delete, ever: archived hides but preserves. 409 archive if ledger- or invoice-linked. One registry serves the library AND ledger/invoice attachments. member_visible is the only member-visibility mechanism; PC reads bypass it." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;spacing=6;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="362" width="380" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
