<mxCell id="p9n11" value="One-way outbound (Management/EC only; PCs cannot send). WhatsApp only to opted-in members via pre-approved template — otherwise recorded as skipped. Email via SES; one WhatsApp Business number per society. DeliveryEntry is the &#x27;member was informed&#x27; audit trail." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;spacing=6;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="900" y="602" width="320" height="110" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
