<mxCell id="p10n3" value="The ONE multi-society component — a separate vendor-owned service (directory.estatly.in), not in any per-society Postgres. PII-free by design: maps tokens/codes → endpoints only; no member names/phones/emails; no central member registry. Public surface is read-only resolve; writes are provisioning-only. Admin panel does not use it." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;spacing=6;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="404" width="360" height="125" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
